sentences: Yoon Son-ha (Korean: 윤손하; born November 17, 1975, Jeonju, Jeollabuk-do, South Korea) is a South Korean actress, singer and television personality (gaijin tarento).
On July 4, 2006, Yoon announced that she got engaged to a Korean entrepreneur who lives in Seoul.
NTV Byoki Wa Nemuranai (Night Hospital / Illness Doesn't Sleep)
